snippet.title: Three Sixty | Dilpreet Dhillon | Parmish Verma | Shipra Goyal | Kaptaan | Desi Crew |Vishakha Dhiman
snippet.description:
Get ready to turn up the energy with “Three Sixty”, an electrifying Punjabi song presented by Speed Records and featuring the powerhouse vocals of Dilpreet Dhillon, Parmish Verma, and Shipra Goyal. This track is packed with high beats, catchy lyrics, and vibrant vibes that make it perfect for parties, celebrations, and non-stop dancing. The collaboration between these popular artists brings a fresh and dynamic flavor to the Punjabi music scene, blending traditional Punjabi rhythms with modern beats for a truly unforgettable listening experience.

Whether you’re looking to boost your playlist with the latest Punjabi hits or want a song that sets the perfect mood for festive gatherings and club nights, “Three Sixty” is the perfect choice. Its high-energy vibe ensures it’s a must-listen for fans of Punjabi music in 2025.

snippet.title: The Bride! | Official Teaser
snippet.description:
There’s a monster inside us all. #TheBrideMovie only in theaters March 6.

From Maggie Gyllenhaal (Academy Award-nominated writer/director of The Lost Daughter) and starring Academy Award nominee Jessie Buckley and Academy Award winner Christian Bale comes THE BRIDE! A bold, iconoclastic take on one of the world’s most compelling stories.

A lonely Frankenstein (Bale) travels to 1930s Chicago to ask groundbreaking scientist Dr. Euphronious (five-time Oscar nominee Annette Bening) to create a companion for him. The two revive a murdered young woman and The Bride (Buckley) is born. What ensues is beyond what either of them imagined: Murder! Possession! A wild and radical cultural movement! And outlaw lovers in a wild and combustible romance!

The film stars Buckley, Bale, Peter Sarsgaard, with Bening, Academy Award nominee Jake Gyllenhaal, and Oscar winner Penélope Cruz. Maggie Gyllenhaal directs from her own screenplay and produces alongside Oscar nominee Emma Tillinger Koskoff, Talia Kleinhendler and Osnat Handelsman Keren. The executive producers are Carla Raij, David Webb and Courtney Kivowitz. 

Gyllenhaal is supported behind the camera by a team of award-winning film artisans, including director of photography Lawrence Sher, production designer Karen Murphy, editor Dylan Tichenor, music supervisor Randall Poster, composer Hildur Gudnadóttir and costume designer Sandy Powell. 

Warner Bros. Pictures Presents A First Love Films / In The Current Company Production, A Maggie Gyllenhaal Film: THE BRIDE!. The film will be distributed worldwide by Warner Bros. Pictures, only in theaters and IMAX in North America on March 6, 2026, and internationally beginning 4 March 2026.

【STORY】
悪魔の心臓を持つ「チェンソーマン」となり、公安対魔特異４課に所属するデビルハンターの少年・デンジ（戸谷菊之介）。
憧れのマキマ（楠木ともり）とのデートで浮かれている中、急な雨に見舞われ、
雨宿りしていると偶然“レゼ”（上田麗奈）という少女と出会った。
近所のカフェで働いているという彼女はデンジに優しく微笑み、二人は急速に親密に。

snippet.title: Ukrainian Jet STRIKE Russian Base – Then THIS Happened...
snippet.description:
A Ukrainian MiG-29, damaged and resource-starved, executes a high-risk cross-border mission into Russian airspace armed with experimental French AASM “Hammer” bombs. After losing one engine to a bird strike, the pilot wrestles with asymmetric control, dwindling fuel, and a radar blind-spot just seconds from catastrophe. Then, at treetop level, he pulls off a 5G escape from unsuspected power lines and presses on to the release point.
In a blistering climb under 6G loads, the weapons control fails, but the pilot manually jettisons the bombs just as a Russian Su-35 fires an R-37M at him. Through split-second reflexes, he evades using chaff, ECM interference, and a notch maneuver.
The bombs navigate a gauntlet of EW jamming, solar interference, wind shear, and point-defense attempts, including S-400 missiles and Pantsir auto cannons, before their seekers lock and deliver devastating, kinetic and shaped-charge impacts on a Russian border guard post.

#ukraine 
#russia 
#beyondmilitary

snippet.title: The Perfect Neighbor | Official Trailer | Netflix
snippet.description:
One woman. Dozens of 911 calls. And a close-knit neighborhood caught in a nightmare. What begins as one woman’s relentless harassment of children spirals into a shocking act of violence. Captured through gripping police bodycam footage, The Perfect Neighbor - Winner of the Sundance Film Festival’s Directing Award - delivers a hauntingly powerful experience that keeps you on edge from start to finish.

Watch on Netflix: https://www.netflix.com/title/82018736

About Netflix:
Netflix is one of the world's leading entertainment services, with over 300 million paid memberships in over 190 countries enjoying TV series, films and games across a wide variety of genres and languages. Members can play, pause and resume watching as much as they want, anytime, anywhere, and can change their plans at any time.

The Perfect Neighbor | Official Trailer | Netflix
https://www.youtube.com/@Netflix

Police bodycam footage reveals how a long-running neighborhood dispute turned fatal in this documentary about fear, prejudice and Stand Your Ground laws.

snippet.title: HAQ | Official Teaser | Yami Gautam Dhar, Emraan Hashmi | Suparn S Varma | In Cinemas 7th Nov
snippet.description:
Shazia Bano takes her husband Abbas to court after he abandons her and their children, sparking a national battle over faith, women’s rights, and justice. Inspired by the landmark Supreme Court judgement of Mohd. Ahmed Khan vs. Shah Bano Begum. Haq is the story of one woman’s fight for her rights and justice. 

Releasing in cinemas on 7th November

HAQ is a fictionalized and dramatized version of events stated in the book titled ‘Bano: Bharat ki Beti’ written by Jigna Vora.

Cast- Yami Gautam, Emraan Hashmi, Vartika Singh, Danish Husain, Sheeba Chadha,
Aseem Hattangady
